sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker (EPP)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC ext-proc
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant KVIndex as KV-Cache Index<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as vLLM Prefiller<br/>(remote)
    participant Decoder as vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP (local)
    participant vLLMEngine as vLLM Engine<br/>ZMQ 5555-5557/TCP

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing (EPP)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
        Gateway->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>9002/TCP
        EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 (ServiceAccount token)
        EPP->>UDS: Tokenize prompt<br/>gRPC over /tmp/tokenizer/*.socket
        UDS-->>EPP: Token IDs
        EPP->>KVIndex: Score endpoints by prefix cache match
        KVIndex-->>EPP: Endpoint scores
        Note over EPP: Run plugins: Filter → Score →<br/>ProfileHandler.Pick → PreRequest
        EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse with<br/>x-prefiller-host-port,<br/>x-encoder-hosts-ports headers
        Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Sidecar,Decoder: Flow 2: P/D Disaggregated Inference (NIXL v2)
        Note over Sidecar: Read x-prefiller-host-port header
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS 1.2+ configurable)
        Note over Prefiller: Execute prefill stage,<br/>compute KV cache
        Prefiller-->>Sidecar: kv_transfer_params<br/>(cache metadata)
        Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/completions<br/>with kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
        Note over Decoder: Transfer KV cache via NIXL,<br/>execute decode/generation
        Decoder-->>Sidecar: SSE stream response
        Sidecar-->>Gateway: SSE stream response
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE stream<br/>generated tokens
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over vLLMEngine,KVIndex: Flow 3: KV-Cache Event Tracking
        vLLMEngine->>EPP: ZMQ PUB/SUB KV events<br/>5555-5557/TCP
        EPP->>KVIndex: Update block index<br/>add/remove/update entries
        Note over KVIndex: Speculative indexing:<br/>predicted entries (TTL 2s)<br/>confirmed by real events
    end
